The below information is partially accurate but deprecated, this is being converted to a watchface.

This reproduces the PDP Screenhack "Munching Squares" for Pebble

This eats tons of battery because it does a lot of screen updates 
ten times per second. So let the user beware.

I'm not sure why it always draws white on black. I'm fairly sure it should 
switch to black on white. This is on the list of things to debug.

http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Munching_square

Hat tip to jwz for the Xscreensaver module that inspired this
